					"value": "Dialog when interactin with the shrine dedicated to Tyrin Stormshore Tabernacle. All players will be able to read some lore about the god. Additionally, if the player is a cleric of Tyr they'll be able to give offerings and pray/communicate with the god to get a blessing."
